{"tid":133451,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"《男朋友的抉擇》政府文員 Vs 律師","createTime":"2017-02-24T15:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T16:15:46.000Z","uid":53272,"like":12,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dbaa8f24f4ba74c1548770917e026b65cfb0b906","tid":133451,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"假設佢地外貌，性格，愛你既程度一樣，無父幹，你會揀邊個呢？<br />\n<br />\n男A<br />\n政府文員<br />\n23月入17k 十年內點都會有30k<br />\n人工按通漲 唔會炒 有保障<br />\n朝9晚6，5days work<br />\n有時可能要輪更星期六日/11am~8pm<br />\n<br />\n男B<br />\n做律師<br />\n23月入四萬 兩年後六萬以上 之後會更多<br />\n頭兩年朝9晚9，5days work<br />\n每個月星期六/日都要翻去ot 3~4次<br />\n第四/五年朝9晚7<br />\n每個月星期六要翻去ot 0~2次<br />\n<br />\na正評<br />\nb負評"},{"pid":"8269ae24fa67dd21cd19620c486d0de14a5b853a","tid":133451,"uid":46649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:34:22.000Z","msg":"律師<br />\n政府文員會磨蝕一個既志氣<br />\n當然 如果係諗住安安穩穩就無所謂啦<br />\n但你將來可能會埋怨你老公<br />\n會諗話點解唔揀律師"},{"pid":"90f022f1d52acfa0f7d3cacb9b3f1c3805f98748","tid":133451,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>律師<br />\n政府文員會磨蝕一個既志氣<br />\n當然 如果係諗住安安穩穩就無所謂啦<br />\n但你將來可能會埋怨你老公<br />\n會諗話點解唔揀律師</blockquote><br />\n咁你想要乜生活先揀律師？"},{"pid":"4083efc678306b772e4a516640875c020a206e08","tid":133451,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:41:23.000Z","msg":"不回答假設性問題"},{"pid":"9966dd7a9869d35a498c873849f0b352a1c3d16f","tid":133451,"uid":75537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T20:01:56.000Z","msg":"做生意嘅<br />\n不嬲價高者得"},{"pid":"4ff4d338f62ec3282a4e49507d5c911ba6c4812f","tid":133451,"uid":58999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T20:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做生意嘅<br />\n不嬲價高者得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a948637a38a6ac52098c864809aad3cdb8f0f466","tid":133451,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor